{"id":222799,"date":"2023-12-11T20:27:22","date_gmt":"2023-12-11T14:57:22","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/?p=222799"},"modified":"2023-12-21T16:31:00","modified_gmt":"2023-12-21T11:01:00","slug":"dhiraj-prasad-sahu","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/","title":{"rendered":"Dhiraj Prasad Sahu Wiki, Age, Caste, Wife, Family, Biography &amp; More"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Prasad-Sahu.jpeg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-223079\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Prasad-Sahu.jpeg\" alt=\"Dhiraj Prasad Sahu\" width=\"473\" height=\"473\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Prasad-Sahu.jpeg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Prasad-Sahu-300x300.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Prasad-Sahu-150x150.jpeg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Prasad-Sahu-65x65.jpeg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 473px) 100vw, 473px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Dhiraj Prasad Sahu is an Indian politician, a veteran member of the Indian National Congress, and a three-time Rajya Sabha MP. In 2023, he hit the headlines after more than Rs. 350 crores were seized from his various premises in the raids by the Income Tax department.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_62 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Contents<\/p>\n<label for=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce4d528d65\" class=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-label\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\"  id=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce4d528d65\"  aria-label=\"Toggle\" \/><nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#WikiBiography\" title=\"Wiki\/Biography\">Wiki\/Biography<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#Physical_Appearance\" title=\"Physical Appearance\">Physical Appearance<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#Family\" title=\"Family\">Family<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#Parents_Siblings\" title=\"Parents &amp; Siblings\">Parents &amp; Siblings<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#Wife_Children\" title=\"Wife &amp; Children\">Wife &amp; Children<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#Address\" title=\"Address\">Address<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#Signature\" title=\"Signature\">Signature<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#Career\" title=\"Career\">Career<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#Controversy\" title=\"Controversy\">Controversy<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#IT_Raids_in_2023\" title=\"IT Raids in 2023\">IT Raids in 2023<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#Car_Collection\" title=\"Car Collection\">Car Collection<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#SalaryIncome\" title=\"Salary\/Income\">Salary\/Income<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#AssetsProperties\" title=\"Assets\/Properties\">Assets\/Properties<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-14\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#Movable_Assets\" title=\"Movable Assets\">Movable Assets<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-15\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#Immovable_Assets\" title=\"Immovable Assets\">Immovable Assets<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-16\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#Net_Worth\" title=\"Net Worth\">Net Worth<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-17\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/#FactsTrivia\" title=\"Facts\/Trivia\">Facts\/Trivia<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WikiBiography\"><\/span>Wiki\/Biography<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Dhiraj Prasad Sahu was born on Monday, 23 November 1959 (<strong>age 64 years; as of 2023<\/strong>) in Lohardaga, Jharkhand. His zodiac sign is Sagittarius. In 1979, he pursued a Bachelor of Arts degree at Marwari College, Ranchi University, Jharkhand.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span>Physical Appearance<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Height (approx.):<\/strong> 5&#8242; 6&#8243;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Weight (approx.):<\/strong> 60 kg<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hair Colour: <\/strong>Black<\/p>\n<p><strong>Eye Colour: <\/strong>Black<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Prasad-Sahus-physical-appearence.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-223078\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Prasad-Sahus-physical-appearence.jpg\" alt=\"Dhiraj Prasad Sahu's physical appearence\" width=\"375\" height=\"507\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Prasad-Sahus-physical-appearence.jpg 444w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Prasad-Sahus-physical-appearence-222x300.jpg 222w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 375px) 100vw, 375px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family\"><\/span>Family<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Parents_Siblings\"><\/span><strong>Parents &amp; Siblings<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Dhiraj Prasad Sahu&#8217;s father, Baldev Prasad Sahu, was a freedom fighter who, after actively participating in the fight for India&#8217;s independence, was given the title Rai Saheb. His mother&#8217;s name is Sushila Devi. He has six brothers. His elder brother, Shivprasad Sahu, was a Congress MP. In 2019, his brother Gopal Sahu contested the Lok Sabha elections from Hazaribagh but lost.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Wife_Children\"><\/span><strong>Wife &amp; Children<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>There is not much information about his wife. He has a son named Harshit.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Address\"><\/span>Address<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Thana Path, P.O. &amp; P.S. &#8211; Lohardaga, Distt. &#8211; Lohardaga, Jharkhand <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_222799_1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_222799_1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.india.gov.in\/my-government\/indian-parliament\/shri-dhiraj-prasad-sahu\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">India.gov.in<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Signature\"><\/span>Signature<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<div id=\"attachment_223051\" style=\"width: 406px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Prasad-Sahus-signature.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-223051\" class=\" wp-image-223051\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Prasad-Sahus-signature.jpg\" alt=\"Dhiraj Prasad Sahu's signature\" width=\"396\" height=\"143\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Prasad-Sahus-signature.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Prasad-Sahus-signature-300x108.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Prasad-Sahus-signature-768x277.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 396px) 100vw, 396px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-223051\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dhiraj Prasad Sahu&#8217;s signature<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span>Career<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Dhiraj Prasad Sahu entered politics on a ticket of the Indian National Congress. In 1979, he became a member of the National Students&#8217; Union of India at Ranchi University and served as its member till 1983. In 1978, he was put behind bars during the Jail Bharo Andolan. Later, he took charge as an office-bearer of the Congress party in the Lohardaga district before joining the Jharkhand Pradesh Congress Committee.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_223077\" style=\"width: 380px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Sahu-greeting-Rahul-Gandhi-at-a-rally-in-Shillong.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-223077\" class=\" wp-image-223077\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Sahu-greeting-Rahul-Gandhi-at-a-rally-in-Shillong.jpg\" alt=\"Dhiraj Sahu greeting Rahul Gandhi at a rally in Shillong\" width=\"370\" height=\"472\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Sahu-greeting-Rahul-Gandhi-at-a-rally-in-Shillong.jpg 470w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Dhiraj-Sahu-greeting-Rahul-Gandhi-at-a-rally-in-Shillong-235x300.jpg 235w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-223077\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dhiraj Sahu greeting Rahul Gandhi at a rally in Shillong<\/p><\/div>\n<p>In May 2009, he contested his maiden Lok Sabha election from the Chatra constituency on a ticket of the Indian National Congress but faced heavy defeat in the election. A month later, i.e., in June 2009, he was elected to the Rajya Sabha in a bypoll; the seat was left empty by Digvijay Singh after he voluntarily resigned from the Rajya Sabha. In 2014, he again contested the Lok Sabha election from the Chatra constituency on a ticket of the Indian National Congress. However, he lost the elections and barely got a little over 16% votes. In May 2018, he preceded Pradeep Kumar Balmuchu to be elected to the Rajya Sabha for the third time from Jharkhand. In addition, he has served as a member of several parliamentary committees including the Standing Committee of Coal, Mines, and Steel, and the Consultative Committee of Power and New &amp; Renewable Energy.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Controversy\"><\/span>Controversy<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"IT_Raids_in_2023\"><\/span>IT Raids in 2023<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>On 6 December 2023, the Income Tax department launched marathon raids against Boudh Distillery Private Limited, an Odisha-based distillery company, and its promoters on charges of tax evasion and unaccounted transactions. The distillery company is owned by Dhiraj Prasad Sahu and his family. A total of Rs. 351 crore cash was found at Dhiraj Prasad Sahu&#8217;s residence in Ranchi. Raids were also carried out at Sabalpur, Bolangir, Titilagarh, Boudh, Sudargarh, Rourkela, and Bhubaneswar. According to some reports, it was the largest cash seizure ever carried out by an agency in India against a single group and businesses associated with it.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_223080\" style=\"width: 587px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Income-Tax-officials-at-Dhiraj-Sahus-residence-compressed.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-223080\" class=\" wp-image-223080\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Income-Tax-officials-at-Dhiraj-Sahus-residence-compressed.jpg\" alt=\"Income Tax officials at Dhiraj Sahu's residence\" width=\"577\" height=\"433\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Income-Tax-officials-at-Dhiraj-Sahus-residence-compressed.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Income-Tax-officials-at-Dhiraj-Sahus-residence-compressed-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Income-Tax-officials-at-Dhiraj-Sahus-residence-compressed-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 577px) 100vw, 577px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-223080\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Income Tax officials at Dhiraj Sahu&#8217;s residence<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Later, Jairam Ramesh, the Congress general secretary, released a statement regarding the issue and said,<\/p>\n<blockquote><p>The Indian National Congress is in no way connected with the businesses of Dheeraj Sahu, MP. Only he can explain, and should explain, how huge amounts of cash have been reportedly unearthed by the Income Tax authorities from his properties.&#8221;<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>Other BJP members alleged Dhiraj of misusing his powers and his close relationship with <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/rahul-gandhi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Rahul Gandhi<\/a>. Deepak Prakash, former BJP State president and Rajya Sabha member, said,<\/p>\n<blockquote><p>This corruption cannot happen without the support of the JMM (Jharkhand Mukti Morcha) government running the state. Congress and corruption have a close relationship. Whenever Congress has come to power, whether it is at the Centre or in State, rampant corruption has taken place. Dhiraj Sahu has a close relationship with Congress leader Rahul Gandhi.&#8221;<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<div>Meanwhile, an old tweet from August 2022, made by Dhiraj Prasad Sahu, went viral on social media in which he expressed his views on black money prevailing in the country even after the demonetisation.<\/div>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"und\" dir=\"ltr\">Dhiraj Prasad Sahu has a dark sense of humour. \ud83d\ude02<a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/hashtag\/CorruptionKiDukan?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">#CorruptionKiDukan<\/a> <a href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/2esDCyip1O\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com\/2esDCyip1O<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&mdash; Amit Malviya (@amitmalviya) <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/amitmalviya\/status\/1733751877219848553?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">December 10, 2023<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https:\/\/platform.twitter.com\/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"><\/script><\/p>\n<p>Later, Prime Minister <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/narendra-modi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Narendra Modi<\/a> brought attention to these raids on Twitter and promised to &#8220;guarantee&#8221; the return of all funds &#8220;looted from the public.&#8221;<\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"hi\" dir=\"ltr\">\u0926\u0947\u0936\u0935\u093e\u0938\u0940 \u0907\u0928 \u0928\u094b\u091f\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u0947 \u0922\u0947\u0930 \u0915\u094b \u0926\u0947\u0916\u0947\u0902 \u0914\u0930 \u092b\u093f\u0930 \u0907\u0928\u0915\u0947 \u0928\u0947\u0924\u093e\u0913\u0902 \u0915\u0947 \u0908\u092e\u093e\u0928\u0926\u093e\u0930\u0940 \u0915\u0947 &#39;\u092d\u093e\u0937\u0923\u094b\u0902&#39; \u0915\u094b \u0938\u0941\u0928\u0947\u0902&#8230; \ud83d\ude02\ud83d\ude02\ud83d\ude02<\/p>\n<p>\u091c\u0928\u0924\u093e \u0938\u0947 \u091c\u094b \u0932\u0942\u091f\u093e \u0939\u0948, \u0909\u0938\u0915\u0940 \u092a\u093e\u0908-\u092a\u093e\u0908 \u0932\u094c\u091f\u093e\u0928\u0940 \u092a\u0921\u093c\u0947\u0917\u0940, \u092f\u0939 \u092e\u094b\u0926\u0940 \u0915\u0940 \u0917\u093e\u0930\u0902\u091f\u0940 \u0939\u0948\u0964 <\/p>\n<p>\u274c\u274c\u274c\ud83d\udcb5 \ud83d\udcb5 \ud83d\udcb5\u274c\u274c\u274c <a href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/O2pEA4QTOj\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com\/O2pEA4QTOj<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&mdash; Narendra Modi (@narendramodi) <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/narendramodi\/status\/1733040901457322300?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">December 8, 2023<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https:\/\/platform.twitter.com\/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"><\/script><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Car_Collection\"><\/span>Car Collection<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>He has four personal vehicles to his name, a BMW, a Fortuner, a Pagero, and a Range Rover.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"SalaryIncome\"><\/span>Salary\/Income<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>In 2018, his annual earning through multiple businesses was estimated to be around Rs 1 crore. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_222799_1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_222799_1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/indianexpress.com\/article\/political-pulse\/dhiraj-sahu-jharkhand-congress-mp-income-tax-raids-odisha-9061596\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Indian Express<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"AssetsProperties\"><\/span>Assets\/Properties<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Movable_Assets\"><\/span><strong>Movable Assets<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Cash: Rs. 15,00,000<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Deposits in Banks, Financial Institutions and Non-Banking Financial Companies: Rs. 2,42,31,965<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Bonds, Debentures and Shares in companies: Rs. 31,16,000<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Immovable_Assets\"><\/span><strong>Immovable Assets<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Non-Agricultural Land: Rs. 2,00,00,000<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Residential Buildings: Rs. 95,00,000<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Note: <\/strong>The given estimates of movable and immovable assets are according to the year 2019. It excludes the assets owned by his wife and dependents. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_222799_1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[3]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_222799_1_3\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/myneta.info\/rajsab09aff\/candidate.php?candidate_id=751\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">My Neta<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Net_Worth\"><\/span>Net Worth<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Dhiraj Prasad Sahu&#8217;s net worth for the year 2019 was estimated to be Rs. 32 crore.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Note:<\/strong> It excludes the net worth of his wife and dependents. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_222799_1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[4]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_222799_1_4\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/myneta.info\/rajsab09aff\/candidate.php?candidate_id=751\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">My Neta<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"FactsTrivia\"><\/span>Facts\/Trivia<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>In 2023, the Ranchi residence of Dhiraj Prasad Sahu that was raided by the Income Tax department was named Sushila Niketan after his late mother, Sushila Devi.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>During the cash counting in the IT raids in 2023, the IT department used dozens of cash-counting machines and involved banks, but a lot of the machines broke down because of the large sum of money.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In November 2022, Sahu participated in <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/rahul-gandhi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Rahul Gandhi<\/a>\u2019s Bharat Jodo Yatra.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Historic <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/hashtag\/BharatJodoYatra?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">#BharatJodoYatra<\/a> ended up winning the hearts of Indians.<\/p>\n<p>Honoured to be a part of this historic journey.<a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/bharatjodo?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">@bharatjodo<\/a> <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/RahulGandhi?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">@rahulgandhi<\/a> <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/INCIndia?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">@incindia<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/hashtag\/RahulGandhi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">#RahulGandhi<\/a> <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/hashtag\/Congress?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">#Congress<\/a> <a href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/L3iDwyWXKx\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com\/L3iDwyWXKx<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&mdash; Dhiraj Prasad Sahu (@dpsahuINC) <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/dpsahuINC\/status\/1621481080128950272?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">February 3, 2023<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https:\/\/platform.twitter.com\/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"><\/script><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Dhiraj Prasad Sahu is the third generation from his family to be associated with the Congress party. <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/indira-gandhi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/url?q=https:\/\/wikibio.in\/indira-gandhi\/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1703227257619000&amp;usg=AOvVaw12S6OLvNUfSGdK_V17G-vL\">Indira Gandhi<\/a> once stayed at his residence in Lohardaga during one of her election campaigns.\u00a0<span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_222799_1_5\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[5]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_222799_1_5\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.thehindu.com\/news\/national\/bjp-targets-congress-over-it-raids-against-dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/article67622464.ece\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Hindu<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Reportedly, Sahu&#8217;s family is involved in many businesses such as liquor, hotels, real estate, transportation, and fisheries.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>According to reports, Dheeraj Sahu&#8217;s father, Baldev, gave the Indian government Rs. 47 lakh and 47 kg of gold after the country&#8217;s independence in 1947 to help boost the economy. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_222799_1_6\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[6]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_222799_1_6\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.indiatoday.in\/india\/story\/dheeraj-sahu-congress-mp-income-tax-department-raids-record-cash-haul-family-background-assets-2474302-2023-12-11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">India Today<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Sahu&#8217;s ancestral home is often referred to as the &#8216;White House of Lohardaga&#8217; due to its important role in Congress&#8217;s political activities. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_222799_1_7\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[7]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_222799_1_7\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.indiatoday.in\/india\/story\/dheeraj-sahu-congress-mp-income-tax-department-raids-record-cash-haul-family-background-assets-2474302-2023-12-11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">India Today<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div><div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_label_expand_222799_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">References<\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_button_plus_222799_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">[+]<\/span><span><\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_button_minus_222799_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button collapsed\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_222799_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">[\u2212]<\/span><\/p><\/div> <div id=\"footnote_references_container_222799_1\" class=\"collapsed\"><table class=\"footnotes_table footnote-reference-container\"><caption class=\"accessibility\">References<\/caption> <tbody> \r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi pointer\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_222799_1_1\" class=\"footnote_backlink\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>1<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.india.gov.in\/my-government\/indian-parliament\/shri-dhiraj-prasad-sahu\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">India.gov.in<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi pointer\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_222799_1_2\" class=\"footnote_backlink\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>2<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/indianexpress.com\/article\/political-pulse\/dhiraj-sahu-jharkhand-congress-mp-income-tax-raids-odisha-9061596\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Indian Express<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_222799_1_3\" class=\"footnote_backlink\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor_222799_1('footnote_plugin_tooltip_222799_1_3');\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>3,<\/a> <a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_222799_1_4\" class=\"footnote_backlink\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor_222799_1('footnote_plugin_tooltip_222799_1_4');\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>4<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/myneta.info\/rajsab09aff\/candidate.php?candidate_id=751\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">My Neta<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi pointer\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_222799_1_5\" class=\"footnote_backlink\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>5<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.thehindu.com\/news\/national\/bjp-targets-congress-over-it-raids-against-dhiraj-prasad-sahu\/article67622464.ece\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Hindu<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_222799_1_6\" class=\"footnote_backlink\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor_222799_1('footnote_plugin_tooltip_222799_1_6');\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>6,<\/a> <a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_222799_1_7\" class=\"footnote_backlink\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor_222799_1('footnote_plugin_tooltip_222799_1_7');\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>7<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.indiatoday.in\/india\/story\/dheeraj-sahu-congress-mp-income-tax-department-raids-record-cash-haul-family-background-assets-2474302-2023-12-11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">India Today<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n <\/tbody> <\/table> <\/div><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Dhiraj Prasad Sahu is an Indian politician, a veteran member of the Indian National Congress, and a three-time Rajya Sabha MP. In 2023, he hit the headlines after more than Rs. 350 crores were seized from his various premises in the raids by the Income Tax department. Wiki\/Biography Dhiraj Prasad Sahu was born on Monday, 23 November 1959 (age 64 years; as of 2023) in Lohardaga, Jharkhand. His zodiac sign is Sagittarius. In 1979, he pursued a Bachelor of Arts degree at Marwari College, Ranchi University, Jharkhand. Physical Appearance Height (approx.): 5&#8242; 6&#8243; Weight (approx.): 60 kg Hair Colour: Black <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":74,"featured_media":223079,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[4],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/222799"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/74"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=222799"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/222799\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":225717,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/222799\/revisions\/225717"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/223079"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=222799"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=222799"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=222799"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}